com.here.android.mpa.cluster

Class ClusterStyle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.here.android.mpa.cluster.ClusterStyle
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicClusterStyle, ImageClusterStyle

    public abstract class ClusterStyle
extends java.lang.Object
    A base class for customizing the look of the cluster icon used for a specific density range. Cluster density represents the number of map markers inside a cluster.

    By default, a cluster is represented on a map by a circular icon with the density drawn in the middle.

    See Also:
    ClusterTheme
